wp:comment.wp:comment_content: Hi, this is a comment. To get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard. Commenter avatars come from Gravatar.

No, absolutely not. Technex is one time purchase with lifetime updates and 6 months of support at no extra costs.

All current and future pre-built websites comes with a single purchase.

Hands-on support with our professional team of support experts is accessible 24/7. You can contact us at the item support tab.

We are an elite author on Envato with a lot of positive feedback from our buyers. All development and support are managed by a team of experienced professionals who love what they do. We are committed to providing the best support and solving almost all issues within 24 hours.
